culture_change.description:
Behavior breads behavior, what are the things we can instill in the company culture to help people be happier and healthier at work?&#13;
&#13;
This article suggests pets, lunch breaks and female bosses among other things.....

the_regenerating_power_of_offering_a_tru.description:
Three suggestions:&#13;
1) remove bad food/beverages from the operating workspaces. &#13;
2) offer a selection of recreational options to get people out during lunch.&#13;
3) install a no disturbing rest time (respected by employees and managers alike).

got_inspiration_board.description:
